  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Feed a Hungry Child in South Africa Today</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Water is life, and as a country with high inequality and large portions of the population living in informal settlements, the water crisis in South Africa has a bigger effect on the poorer people who rely on agriculture for an income. Our goal is to implement innovative and sustainable water solutions to schools around the country, helping to relieve them of their dependency on large amounts of water for agriculture, as well as helping to provide self-sustaining meals to students all year.</narrative>
  </description>
